description: Hlangana ne-platform yethu futhi wenze okuningi ngezinsizakalo zethu zokwenziwe yi-AI
f_header_desc: I-Architects Platform isisombululo sokuqala esenziwe ukucela izinselele nokukhula amakhono abaqashi abanjini.
f_content_desc: Yi-platform eqondisiwe yi-AI eyenza abanolwazi nabathandi ezinkundleni zezobusekelo nokwenziwe ngokunikeza uchungechunge olufanayo lwezici zomsebenzi nezinto.
f_tabs_1_desc: I-platform yethu isiza abaqashi ukudala imibono yokunqulwa, ukunikeza impendulo nokucela amacebo angaphandle.
f_tabs_2_desc: Siyasiza ukudala imibono eyakhayo, ukunikeza ukuzindla nokwenza ukulungisa imibono yakho yokuqala ngokuxoxa impendulo.
f_tabs_3: Ukuhlaziwa Umshiso we-Market Trend nokuQikelela Izikhwama
f_tabs_3_desc: I-Architects Platform igcina uhlelo lokuhlela imali ngokusiza ekudaleni izinga ezithile nezamabhudget ezichanezelayo kumaphrojekthi wazobusekelo.
fb_item_1: Umqondo wokunqulwa wokuqala nemibono yokunqulwa ejabulisayo
fb_item_1_desc: Uhlelo kufanele lunikeze umqondo wokunqulwa osekwe ufakwe ngumqashi ezidingeni zomkhiqizi nezinye izinselele njengendawo, ibhudget futhi futhi kudale imibono yokunqulwa ejabulisayo.
fb_item_2_desc: Abasebenzisi bazokwazi ukufinyelela ezimboneni zokudweba nokudweba ezakhiwe ngaphakathi lapho bangakwazi khona ukunikeza imibono yabo ku-Architect ukuze bathole impendulo, imibono nokuguqulwa kokunqulwa.
fb_item_3_desc: U-Architect usiza ekudaleni izimboni zezindlu nezakhiwo ngokunikeza imibono kanye nokusethwa kwezinto nezesekeli ngesikhombo nje kuphela ngaphandle kokudinga nokudweba konke.
fb_item_4: Ukudalwa kokudweba kwangaphakathi nokugcwalwa kwezesekeli okwenziwe ngok
fb_item_4_desc: Imizila eyenziwe epulatifomu kanye neyalethwe abasebenzisi njengezithombe izozodweba ngokwengeziwe ngezithombe ezingoqinile ngaphakathi kwemizuzwana.
fb_item_5_desc: U-Architect uzosiza ekudaleni nokuguqula imibono esenziwe kakade kanye nemizila ngokususelwa kwesisombululo futhi futhi unikeza imibono nokuguquguquka kokunqulwa.
fb_item_6: Ukuhlaziwa Umshiso we-Market Trend nokuQikelela Izikhwama
fb_item_6_desc: Ngokwemibono nemibandela yedingo yedijitali, i-Architect isiza ngokuhlalutya izidingo zokunqulwa nokulinganisa izindleko zokwakha futhi isikisela izisombululo ezithengisayo kakhulu.
h_header_desc: I-platform eqondisiwe yi-AI esiza futhi inikeza amandla abanolwazi nabathandi ezinkundleni zezobusekelo nokwenziwe ngokunikeza uchungechunge olufanayo lwezici zomsebenzi nezinto.
mb_header_desc: Hlala ubukele, yenza umklamo futhi uqhubekele umsebenzi phambili ne-Architects ku-iOS ne-Android. Landa uhlelo namhlanje.
pr_header_desc: Lapha ku-Innovate Fusion sigxile kubaqashi lapho ubuchwepheshe, ukuhlaziya nokukhulisa ingxenye yemali kungachaza inani elide futhi kubekele phambili ukwanda kwezomnotho.
r_header_desc: Faka ikheli ye-imeyili oyisebenzise ngayo lapho ubhalisele i-akhawunti yakho, futhi sizothumela ikheli lokusetha kabusha iphasiwedi yakho.
